title: Daz3D - Poser Tools
description:
Daz|Studio and Poser Tools.


The First in a series of Daz3D and Poser Torrents, the DAZ|Studio and Poser Tools Pack is a selection of Tools that I have collected and used over the past to create content for DAZ|Studio. The enclosed tools will help provide new clothing, textures, lights, etc. for your favorite characters in your favored application.

Included:

Clothing Morphkits for V3 and V4
Crossdresser 2.5.1 with several licenses, including V4!
Studio Light Pro
Light Dome Pro
Mood Master
Injection Magic
UTC with several character plugins
SkinVUE6.1 with Poser and DAZ plugins
Tailor 1.61
Mask Creator
Mimic Pro
The Pose Tools for Poser

....and MUCH more!


As always, please seed and if you like it, buy it!
